      "StudentZoneDescription": "<h2>Students Downloads</h2><hr><p style=\"line-height: 1;\">1.Documents to be attached with application form for issuance of Different Certificates<a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/studentDocument/downloads/Documents to be attached with application form for issuance of Different Certificates.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/studentDocument/downloads/Documents to be attached with application form for issuance of Different Certificates.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Click here to view</a></p><p><br></p><p>2.Application Form for Special Examination <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/SE_Form_2016_30Nov2016.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/fb529b97-28d7-4f2c-8b77-433065d4dfcc\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>3.Format for Case of Unfair Means <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/cukashmir/departmentdocs_36/FormatUM.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/4b43e59a-76d3-4273-bfc7-36bf0b3d0b21\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>4.Form for Admission to Integrated / Masters Programmes</p><p><a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/AdmissionFormPG27July2015(6).pdf\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/1a64b814-cbef-40c5-8e46-7202cff69b64\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>5.Admission Form for Research Programmes <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/cukashmir/departmentdocs_36/AdmissionFormResearchProgrammes.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/d3d54ee7-fa40-4c62-a55b-50c5239c0d7e\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>6.Hostel Application Form <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/HostelApplicationForm_02Aug2014.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/40a5baac-e269-47b7-8739-4f3242c160d3\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>.7.Application Form for Semester Admission <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/SemesterAdmissionForm.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/2ba44a77-4c80-40fd-8d87-4874b82e1046\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>8.Application Form for ESE <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/Examination%20Form_Revised.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/037c4563-0d8f-4df5-95be-4d5a77d4bbdf\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>9.Application Form for Re-evaluation <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/AppFormRe_evaluation_07Feb2014.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/03994a69-598e-4a70-8594-b1b65916befe\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>10.Application Form for obtaining photocopies of evaluated Answer Scripts <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/AppFormPhotocopiesAnswerScripts28Feb2014.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/0c1dee6b-e85c-45d8-8989-a38485e2238f\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\">11.Application Form for Condonation Attendance Shortage <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/AppFormCondonationAttendShortage07Feb2014.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;</a></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/AppFormCondonationAttendShortage07Feb2014.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>12.Application Form for Division Improvement <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/AppFormDivisionImprovement07Feb2014.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/25fb3fad-8d21-41c4-9a0e-443ffb611eb2\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>13.Application Form for issuance of Result Status Certificate <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/AppFormResultStatusCert_07Feb2014.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/45f84d69-13fd-4cfb-81c5-ce836195977e\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&n