idedFund19March2014.docx.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/2a349f39-b7c9-457e-b4ad-ee5fe42d4066\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>19.Application Form for Social Orientation Elective <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/SOEForm19March2014.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/efac3ed3-72ac-49e5-baa2-444773b2a049\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>20.Application Form for Degree In-Absentia <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/convocation%20form.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/08ab23eb-234b-4601-a30f-b52b8a1e2f82\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a>&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>21.Registration Form for Institutional E-mail ID <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/scholarEmail.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/ba26c0cb-5203-413e-92fc-c0fece0ef217\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a>&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>22.Wi-Fi Registration Form <a href=\"http://disgenonline.in/cukapi/p/docs/WiFi-Form.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><br><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" alt=\"\" src=\"blob:http://cukadmin.disgenonline.in/01bd10e6-99fc-45fe-8f85-ca973386d6be\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-fr-old-src=\"data:image/png;base64,\">&nbsp;Click here to view</a> &n