.ac.in/teaching-evaluation/ESE_December2010.aspx\" target=\"_parent\"><u>Result of End Semester Examination, December 2010</u></a></li></ul><p><u><br></u></p><p><u><br></u></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>",
